CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 5, 1956, pg. A2 reads: "Testimonial Banquet - Among the guests at the speaker's table at the testimonial banquet honoring Dr. Joseph A. Randall in Clairton Saturday night were, left to right: Mrs. Charles Bookert, Mayor Kenneth Stilley, W.P. Young, Dr. Randall, his wife, Mrs. Randall, and Gordon B. Hicks. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men, and women including woman on far left wearing polka dot dress, seated at rectangular banquet tables in interior for Dr. Joseph A. Randall testimonial dinner, Clairton
